2. applyChangesToRelease0.9  and updateGET_PARAMETER.gawk 
   changes:
     Laplace_SOT -> Simple_SOT
     ProblemVec->ProblemStat
     ProblemInstatVec->ProblemInstat
     GET_PARAMETER(...)->Parameters::get(...)
   details see in  updateGET_PARAMETER.gawk

